800
00:29:38,380 --> 00:29:39,560
 I tu Isus je Hrist.

801
00:29:39,560 --> 00:29:41,820
 On u meni, ja u njemu.

802
00:29:41,820 --> 00:29:44,140
 Tu je Bog.

803
00:29:44,140 --> 00:29:46,580
 I tu bili meni.

804
00:29:46,580 --> 00:29:49,680
 Jednostavno, to to.

805
00:29:49,680 --> 00:29:52,500
 On u meni, ja u njemu.

806
00:29:52,500 --> 00:29:54,700
 Taj sanduk, ne ne zna,

807
00:29:54,700 --> 00:29:58,220
 da li u zlato ili drvo?

808
00:29:58,220 --> 00:30:03,100
 I tu objašnil mi na svoj način,

809
00:30:03,100 --> 00:30:04,240
 na arabski jezik,

810
00:30:04,240 --> 00:30:05,120
 tu bili meni.

811
00:30:05,760 --> 00:30:07,920
 ta pitanja i tu to i prehvatio

812
00:30:07,920 --> 00:30:09,420
 za veke vekova.

813
00:30:09,420 --> 00:30:13,800
 Nemam više ta sumlja.

814
00:30:13,800 --> 00:30:14,340
 Ali

815
00:30:14,340 --> 00:30:16,640
 uvijek

816
00:30:16,640 --> 00:30:18,680
 čovjek

817
00:30:18,680 --> 00:30:21,380
 vagat

818
00:30:21,380 --> 00:30:23,140
 sebi sam.

819
00:30:23,140 --> 00:30:26,600
 Znači,

820
00:30:26,600 --> 00:30:29,500
 vraćamo tamo

821
00:30:29,500 --> 00:30:30,980
 od početka,

822
00:30:30,980 --> 00:30:32,520
 da

823
00:30:32,520 --> 00:30:35,540
 Isus

824
00:30:35,540 --> 00:30:37,400
 danas svidoči pred vama,

825
00:30:37,400 --> 00:30:38,280
 hoču vama,

826
00:30:38,280 --> 00:30:39,100
 kako meni,

827
00:30:39,100 --> 00:30:40,060
 njega

828
00:30:40,060 --> 00:30:41,400
 hvalam

829
00:30:41,400 --> 00:30:42,500
 i slavam

830
00:30:42,500 --> 00:30:43,740
 i klanjim se.

831
00:30:43,740 --> 00:30:44,700
 Zašto?

832
00:30:44,700 --> 00:30:46,800
 Zato spasim mi od tamo.

833
00:30:46,800 --> 00:30:49,180
 Spasim mi od

834
00:30:49,180 --> 00:30:49,700
 poka

835
00:30:49,700 --> 00:30:50,400
 o životu.

836
00:30:50,400 --> 00:30:52,820
 Ono, što danas

837
00:30:52,820 --> 00:30:54,240
 kažem za sebi sam,

838
00:30:54,240 --> 00:30:54,960
 kao

839
00:30:54,960 --> 00:30:55,640
 bez šečer

840
00:30:55,640 --> 00:30:56,160
 gorka,

841
00:30:56,160 --> 00:30:57,840
 a život

842
00:30:57,840 --> 00:30:58,740
 bez Isus

843
00:30:58,740 --> 00:31:00,000
 mračno

844
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:01,160
 i jadno.

845
00:31:03,160 --> 00:31:04,180
 za hvaliom,

846
00:31:04,180 --> 00:31:04,860
 hvala

847
00:31:04,860 --> 00:31:05,200
 Isus

848
00:31:05,200 --> 00:31:05,820
 i Marija,

849
00:31:05,820 --> 00:31:07,400
 njega

850
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:07,680
 Bog

851
00:31:07,680 --> 00:31:08,000
 vas

852
00:31:08,000 --> 00:31:08,860
 blagoslovi

853
00:31:08,860 --> 00:31:10,280
 i pazi

854
00:31:10,280 --> 00:31:11,060
 i čuva.

855
00:31:11,060 --> 00:31:12,280
 Hvala vam

856
00:31:12,280 --> 00:31:12,660
 plnou.

857
00:31:12,660 --> 00:31:13,740
 Hvala.

858
00:31:13,740 --> 00:31:15,740
 Hvala.

